# 1932 Emperor's Cup

Statistics of Emperor's Cup in the 1932 season.
Overview
It was contested by 3 teams, and Keio Club won the cup.
Results
Semi-finals
*Keio Club 3–0 Sakai Secondary School Club
Final
*Keio Club 5–1 Yoshino Club
Keio Club won the cup.
